              <p>Access a curated marketplace of pre-built AI agents for every business vertical.</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn">Explore Marketplace <i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i></a>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <span class="card-num">03</span>
              <div class="card-img-wrap">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587560699334-bea93391dcef?q=80&w=1170&auto=format&fit=crop"
